sequenceDiagram
    participant E as Executor
    participant D as DAL118
    participant S as SWA723
    participant U as UAL492
    participant R as Runway

    Note over E: T=0: Poll all tasks
    D->>E: Pending (approaching)
    S->>E: Pending (preparing)
    U->>E: Pending (approaching)

    Note over E: T=2: SWA723 ready
    S->>R: Request runway
    R-->>S: Cleared (runway clear)

    Note over E: T=4: SWA723 airborne
    S->>R: Release runway

    Note over E: T=5: DAL118 requests
    D->>R: Request runway
    R-->>D: Cleared
